            <title>[GROOVY-2530] Simple script results in VerifyError</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2530</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running the following fails with VerifyError:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;while (def obj = 2){&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;</description>
